This paper discusses privacy protection in electronic medical records, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and database systems (cs.DB). The proposed feature ablation method involves machine learning techniques, which can also be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the topic of electronic medical records and privacy is relevant to the field of healthcare (cs.HC).
